Just plain bad. Mass produced beer taste with a fancy name and fancy label. No better than MC.

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

beer_brewer_name: Portland Brewing Company (Pyramid - North American Breweries)
review_blob: Decent brew. A lot lighter then the appearance would like you to believe. Good flavor and easy to drink. It does have a slight carbonization, which is kind of odd.
Not sure why this beer does not get better ratings. This is one of my favs. Easy drinking and smooth, with a bit of a hoppy bite after. Great everyday brew.
beer_name: Oskar Blues Mamas Little Yella Pils

review_blob: Excellent smooth, easy drinking beer. This is one of my go to beers after a long work day.
Just discovered this at whole foods. Recommended by an employee there. What a great find. Excellent hoppy taste. Smooth drinking. Go out and get it.
Excellent aroma and awesome coconut flavor. I am not a huge porter fan, but this one is excellent. Lovin the beer in cans.....the way it should be.
Just loving the Maui brewing co beers, after recently discovering this brand. Fantasic ipa, great flavor. Love the cans.
My favorite ipa so far. I had this on tap at the Deschutes brew pub in portland. Fantastic. Great color, great hoppy taste.
